type(scope): concise summary

- describe the first concrete change
- describe the second concrete change
- note verification or follow-up when relevant

# Type must be one of:
# feat, fix, chore, docs, test, refactor, perf, ci
#
# Examples:
# feat(ingestion): add watermark lookback handling
#
# - persist high-water mark in DuckDB control table
# - apply CSV/API lower-bound filtering during incremental runs
# - verify with make clean run and make test
